name: Laharl
description:
An arrogant Overlord who is always trying to prove he is the strongest demon in the Netherworld.
He may look a little frail, but don't underestimate him.
This diminutive demon is capable of exceeding 530K Power.
He doesn't wash his hands after going to the toilet.
He plays 100 hours of video games each day.
He takes whatever he wants.
And that's not all. As the ruler of the Netherworld, he is the epitome of evil.
※ Good kids should stay away!

name: Killia
description:
After Void Dark killed his lover, he became a loner filled with hatred whose only goal was to seek revenge.
However, an encounter with real friendship changed him.
He is Goldion's favorite student and the successor to the Ultimate Demon Techniques.
To everyone's surprise, he became a fighter who also has a great love for cooking.
His specialty is curry.
He has a naughty side and sometimes likes to eat during battle.

name: Valvatorez
description:
Valvatorez is a Prinny Instructor in Hades, the Nether Prison.
He was once a powerful demon who was feared as a Tyrant and a vampire.
Eventually, he made a promise to never drink human blood again.
Now that he can't drink blood, sardines are his favorite food.
He believes sardines help him regain some of the power he can no longer get from drinking blood.

name: Adell
description:
Adell is a very honest, passionate boy who always does whatever he knows to be right.
He never breaks a promise, because it is not his style.
Due to a previous psychological trauma, he has a deep fear of women. 
Luckily, Rozalin has helped him make progress in this regard.
Family means a lot to him. 
However, it seems he is too shy to ask Rozalin to marry him...

name: Mao
description:
Mao is a genius with an Evil Quotient of 1.8 million.
He is both the Dean of the Evil Academy and the No.1 Freshman Leader. Although Raspberyl is Mao's archrival, they actually maintain a close relationship.
He loves human experimentation and body modification.
Whenever he discovers something to experiment on, he starts breathing heavily and making strange noises. Not soon after, he also starts to drool.

name: Etna
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Fallen Angel Flonne
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Seraphina
description:
Seraphina is the Gorgeous Overlord. 
She is the wealthiest being in the Netherworld, Celestia and the Human World.
She is extremely beautiful and her "Balor Gaze" can make any male become her slave.
She met Killia while fighting Void Dark and quickly fell in love with him.
She is always thinking of ways to charm Killia in order to make him her minion.

name: Fuka Kazamatsuri
description:
Fuka is a student 
at St. Goliath 3-B.
After she was killed, she was supposed to become a Prinny, but there weren't enough Prinny hides, so she remained a human.
She won't admit to having died and stubbornly believes that everything around her is a dream.
The average person 
can only release 30% of their potential%, but her Power of Belief enables her to reach her full 100%.

name: Rozalin
description:
Rozalin is Overlord Zenon's only daughter. She has lived most of her life in a massive mansion and thus, grew up unaware of the world's suffering.
However, her true identity is... (TBC)
She has spent a lot of time with Adell, from whom she's constantly trying to get away. 
She has totally not in any way fallen in love with him at all.
This romantic comedy has gone on for quite some time. 
After the two completed their own adventure, they returned home  together and are basically a couple.
She was born to the Snow clan, and is very haughty.

name: Axel
description:
Axel was once a famous demon known by many as the Dark Hero.
However, his popularity has waned over the years and he is somewhat of a has-been.
This happens to many famous entertainers. Axel is rather 
sad he can't go back to his former glory days.
Until this day, he has ignored the cold eyes of others. One day, he will return to the stage and reign as the king of rock forever.

name: Fenrich
description:
Fenrich is a werewolf and Valvatorez's butler.
He once was hired to assassinate Valvatorez, but failed because he was impressed by Valvatorez's magnanimous appeal.
He then vowed to remain loyal to his new master until the day he died.
As a ruthless strategist, he will do whatever he can to help Valvatorez be seen as the strongest Demon in the Netherworld.

name: Majorita
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Emizel
description:
Emizel, son of the Death King, followed in his father's footsteps and became the 63rd President of the Netherworld.
He once was the leader of the president's elite task force, as well as an enemy of Valvatorez and Fenrich, but now they are good friends.

name: Barbara
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Girl Laharl
description:
Laharl once accidentally turned into a girl.
Although he looked different, it was still the same old Laharl inside.
"C'mon, this is ridiculous!"
Apparently, some of Laharl's diehard fans were less than happy with this plot development.

name: Christo
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Zeroken
description:
Zeroken is known as the man who revived the Ultimate Demon Techniques.
In the past, he was a 
timid teenager who worshiped Goldion, but eventually he became an Overlord who fights for those he cherishes.
All modern martial art techniques in the Netherworld 
are branches of the Ultimate Demon Techniques, bearing witness to his extraordinary achievements.

name: Red Magnus
description:
Red Magnus is the Overlord of the Scorching Flame.
He is a natural super-fighter who believes power is everything.
His own underlings once betrayed him because they thought he was too capricious.
He became a much calmer individual after meeting Killia.
Magnus once made Killia his eternal rival, but the two are still on good terms.

name: King Krichevskoy
description:
King Krichevskoy is Laharl's dad and 
an ally of Lamington, the High Seraph of Celestia.
He is regarded as a great Netherworld ruler. 
No one has ever matched his strength and personality. 
He is loved by many.
He is also the only demon Etna admires.

name: Sicily
description:
Sicily is an Angel who came from Celestia to become an Overlord.
She claims she is King Krichevskoy's daughter and Laharl's sister.
"She is both an angel and the daughter of a demon? 
What's the deal!?"
Any players who are wondering what the answer to this question is, please play DISGAEA D2.

name: Almaz
description:
One day, a timid hero 
came to the Evil Academy. 
He encountered various incidents in the Netherworld 
after meeting Mao. 
After going through all that, he grew a lot and eventually 
blossomed into a true hero! 
He is now living a sweet married life 
with Princess Sapphire.

name: Master Big Star
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Salvatore
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Sapphire
description:
She is a princess in the Human World.
She may appear as a delicate princess, but is actually a fierce warrior who vowed 
to defeat the Overlord before the Overlord 
had a chance to kidnap her! 
She is also a born killing machine 
that annihilates any demon on sight! 
She calls herself a "somewhat robust princess".

name: Nemo
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Bloodis
description:
A Demon General who's been called 
the right-hand man of Void Dark the Demon Emperor. 
It is rumored that he is by far the most powerful Demon General, and his overwhelming fighting ability 
is second only to Void Dark. 	
Loyal to Void Dark, the black-armored Demon General 
continues to carry out his duties today 
in a chilly manner.

name: Nagi
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Rutile
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Stella
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Xenolith
description:
Xenolith is a mysterious and reserved red-haired Demon.
He has awesome magic abilities and is believed to be as strong as an Overlord.
He has spent a lot of time trying to protect his sister, Etna. 
Don't ever try talking to him.

name: Apprentice Angel Flonne
description:
Flonne was once sent from Celestia by Lamington to assassinate King Krichevskoy.
However, shortly after her arrival, she was caught by Laharl and Etna. 
After a series of events, they then became partners.
She is obsessed with the concept of "love".
She is frequently called a "Love Freak" due to how she never stops talking about it.

name: Pure Flonne
description:
This is Flonne's form that looks like Pure Pink from the 
Pure Seven Morphing Angels TV show.
When she looks like this, she possesses Archangel powers.
Why? Because of love!
There is no problem that the 
power of love can't resolve!

name: Archangel Flonne
description:
After Vulcanus died (erm... huh?), Flonne was made into a temporary Archangel!
This promotion 
shocked everyone in Celestia. 
Everyone wondered what Lamington's intentions were.
Please take a look at 
the final EP of Archangel Flonne: The Way of the Archangel!

name: Void Dark
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Angel Artina
description:
In the Human World, Artina was a nurse and a nun. 
When she died, she became an Angel and spent her time stealing money from Demons. This earned her the title "Angel of Avarice".
On the battlefield, she will try to save everyone, even if they're an enemy.
It is because of Artina that the powerful Vampire Tyrant Valvatorez gave up drinking human blood.

name: Nurse Artina
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Tyrant Valvatorez
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Tyrant Overlord Killidia
description:
Killidia is the Overlord of the Cryo Blood Netherworld.
He was once tyrannical and invincible, but Goldion cut him down to size.
After spending time with Goldion and his daughter Liezerota, the coldness in his heart eventually melted.
However, this encounter led to a greater tragedy...

name: Awakened Killia
description:
Awakened Killia is 
Tyrant Overlord Killidia's form after his cold heart thawed.
Once his evil heart 
was cleansed of all 
anger, hatred, and sorrow, Killia obtained real power and 
mastered the ultimate skill of 
the Ultimate Demon Techniques!!

name: Etna [Color Versions]
description:
These are Etna's clones.
Each clone is as strong as Etna, so don't think they will be defeated easily.
It's easy to see how much enthusiasm the developers have for this version!
Perhaps one day, DISGAEA will also be a fighting game…

name: Skirt Version Etna (Majin Etna)
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Asagi
description: Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh

name: Captain Gordon, Defender of Earth
description:
Gordon is the 37th Defender of Earth.
He first met Laharl 
when the Earth Defense Force 
sent him to the Netherworld to wipe out the Overlord.
He is seen by many as a bumbling and incompetent buffoon.
Nevertheless, he 
never fails to save the day.
He likes to eat Pizza Shack's 
Teriyaki Pizza.

name: Jennifer
description:
Jennifer is Captain Gordon's blonde assistant.
Without knowing her, Jennifer may just seem like eye candy, but she is in fact a 
super talented genius 
who developed an invincible robot when she was 5 and got a 
doctorate when she was 10.
Some say she is also really good at martial arts.

name: Mr. Champloo
description:
Champloo is a Home Economics teacher at the Evil Academy and a master of High Heat-Style Chaos-School Kitchen Fist.
"Cooking comes from the heart!
Cooking means always risking your life! You must be passionate about cooking and use the right ingredients. Boom!"
This is his personal philosophy.

name: Yukimaru
description:
Like Rozalin, Yukimaru was born to the Snow Clan.
Yukimaru first met Rozalin and Adell when she was searching for Zenon to avenge the destruction of her village.
She is a powerful ninja, but her sense of responsibility often gets her in difficult situations.
A young ninja.

name: Fubuki
description:
Yukimaru's older brother.
Fubuki is a dangerous ninja. 
To avenge his clan, he is willing to do anything and 
once fought against Adell.
In a previous battle, he lost his eyesight. 
However, with his determined nature, he has been able to keep 
improving his ninjutsu.
His voice actor is Takehito Koyasu, who himself is a 
big fan of DISGAEA.

name: Zenon
description:
As the God of All Overlords, he is greatly feared and many Overlords want to kill him.
He is the Overlord of Overlords.
It is extremely difficult to determine how strong this individual is.
However, he chose to be reincarnated after getting tired of fighting and killing.
After reincarnation, he became Rozalin.

name: Justice Flonne
description:
Fallen Angel Flonne 
liked Prism Rangers too much 
and turned into Justice Flonne.
In this form, she doesn't seem too different from her Apprentice Angel form. 
"I can feel myself
getting stronger and more courageous!"
She can already say things like this.

name: Kurtis
description:
The appearance of Kurtis during his lifetime.
He lost 70% of his body 
in an "incident", and is now 
mostly a mechanized cyborg.
Although he and Gordon have 
had their clashes, they are now 
comrades in arms. 
With hot blood wrapped in a steel body, he's determined to eliminate all evil!

name: Don Joaquin
description:
The first Defender of Earth who is said 
to have left for the Netherworld 
to defeat the Overlord but never returned. 
He became a ghost in the Netherworld 
and stood in the way of Laharl, but eventually he fulfilled his long-time wish as a Hero 
and passed away. 
Now, he has emerged as the heroic spirit 
of the Defender of Earth!
He targets the Overlord but has many demon friends, and he is kind to everyone 
except the Overlord. 
He may look like an ordinary old man, but his hidden power is the real deal!

name: Christo
description:
He says he is an Overlord from what he claims is a "certain giant Netherworld".
He is an extremely skilled and ruthless war strategist and will do anything to win a battle.
Somehow, he knows a lot about Celestia. 
In order to help those in the Netherworld understand what Christmas is, he has been preparing gifts for everyone.
But he becomes very worried as things go wrong.

name: Mage Noel
description:
Noel has been greatly influenced by the books she has read about the ways of the Human World. 
She really loves Santa.
To her, it truly is amazing that Santa is able to deliver gifts to people all over the world in one night.
However, she has developed a crazy belief that Santa became a superhuman by delivering gifts and that she can also become a more powerful wizard by imitating him.
With Christmas approaching in the Netherworld, she thinks its a good idea to help Christo so she can learn the secrets of Santa.

name: Majorita
description:
On the hunt for Christmas gifts, this former Demon General appeared before Laharl and the others.
Majorita eventually cast a 
curse on herself that would resurrect her.
Although she looks quite cute, she is not at all weak.
Why does Majorita 
want a gift.....

name: Prinny Kurtis
description:
As a human, Kurtis sacrificed himself in a battle 
and ended up as a green Prinny. 
Even as a Prinny, he is still a Defender of Earth.
His heroic character 
has gained the admiration of many Prinnies, who all call him 
"Green Bro!"
He has worked hard to copy the way 
Prinnies speak by saying "dood" at the end of every sentence in order to get along with them.
He still feels trapped in his new Prinny body and is 
working on a way to become human again.

name: Dark Adonis Mid-Boss
description:
A narcissistic demon
who sees Laharl as a rival 
and is always up for a fight.
Don't judge him on his name. 
When he met Laharl the first time, he exclaimed:
"Just call me Mid-Boss!"
Ever since that encounter, 
this name has stuck to him. 
He hasn't been able to change this situation either.
After receiving Laharl's invite to 
decide who the strongest Demon is, he decides to go, but what is his true intention...?

name: Rainier
description:
Born to a family of treasure hunters, she has a knack for hunting treasure. 
She did not recognize Laharl's status as an Overlord at first, but now she seems to have accepted it. Maybe. 
She claims to have babysat Laharl when he was a child and that Laharl loved to act like a spoiled baby. The accuracy of this claim seems to be a matter of fierce debate.

name: Kyoko Needleworker
description:
One of Raspberyl's lackeys who enjoys needlework. 
She is well versed in the legends of the academy and can play the role of commentator without a hitch. 
With her ninja-level stealth, she has been spreading rumors about the legendary graduate Raspberyl without the students realizing it. 
She's always working with Asuka Cranekick, another lackey of Raspberyl, and they spend their days praising Raspberyl together.

name: Asuka Cranekick
description:
Another of Raspberyl's lackeys who likes to send Paper Cranes to opponents after beating them up. 
She is a quiet, naturally polite young lady. 
She looks like she keeps a memoir of the legendary delinquency of Raspberyl and reads it to the students. 
Because of her blind faith in Raspberyl, she shows no mercy towards anyone who harbors ill will toward her and will dispatch them on sight. 
Dispatch to where, you ask? 
Well, you don't really want to know...

name: Saint Etna
description:
A demon that looks just like Etna 
who has suddenly shifted into this world. 
Her soft-spoken manner 
and her white costume 
give the impression of a saint. 
Who is she and 
what is her purpose?

name: Fuka XENO
description:
A girl who came from nowhere 
and looks exactly like Fuka. 
However, she's got different skin color and clothes, as well as a different personality. 
Why she showed up 
in front of Fuka and the others 
remains a mystery. 
XENO is read exactly as it's spelled, thanks for asking.

name: Desco XENO
description:
The ultimate weapon, she looks identical to Desco and came here along with Fuka XENO. 
The way she calls Fuka XENO "Big Sis" 
with fondness resembles Fuka and Desco, but the way she looks at Saint Etna with coldness and evil in her eyes is nothing like Desco. 
The XENO in her name is read just like the one in her sister's.

name: Love Oracle
description:
A Magic Cutie who claims to have been born in a dandelion.
He's actually a boy who plays a Magic Cutie for fun! 
Love Oracle never gives up.
For himself, and for the pride of all Magic Cuties! 
Who the Celestia is Love Oracle? 
Will his true identity be revealed one day?

name: Takashi Boy
description:
The true face of Love Oracle the Magic Cutie upon losing everything. 
His costume, on which Takashi spent a whole month's allowance, has been rent asunder by its violent requisition at the hands of Darktina. 
Poor Love Oracle. Keep it together, Takashi.

name: Virunga
description:
Archangel from Celestia. 
He is quite beautiful, unlike a certain evil-looking beard-face (according to Etna). 
A talented person who uses his wisdom and tactics 
to defend order in Celestia, but why is he in the Netherworld, and in a Cat Cafe?

name: Barbara
description:
A demon who was once an Overlord Candidate.
Born into a family of venerable knights, she believes in following her Lord's orders faithfully and obeys any command. 
She's called an Order-Taking Demon, and will turn the tables on you if your instructions are not specific enough. But Barbara never acts through her own will. So why is she here in the Cat Cafe?

name: Vato Brothers
description:
Demon Chewie, who includes "ese" at the end of every line he says. 
Demon Cholo, who includes "homes" at the end of every line he says. 
Demon Churro, who includes "weddo" at the end of every line he says. 
The three of them are called Vato Brothers! 
Don't you say we are the same. 
Freshmen of Evil Academy 
and classmates with Mao and Sapphire.

name: Iron-blooded Ayame
description:
She made herself a name among the freshmen 
during Mao the Dean's absence. 
When provoked, she'll subdue her opponents 
with her fists in one-on-one duels 
on the riverbank. 
With her strength, good looks 
and cool temperament, she is very popular 
even among female students. 
The male student uniform is her favorite daily dress.

name: Sister Artina
description:
The appearance of Artina when she was alive as a human being. 
During her life, she was an innocent and virtuous nun who healed the wounded of war and saved the lives of many soldiers, both allies and enemies. 
She also has a compassionate heart that treats demons kindly and without prejudice.

name: Creator Asagi
description:
She appeared like a comet
at this year's MGS
with her new VR game.
Cheerful and energetic,
she won the hearts of the organizers and
thus got the best spot.
In spite of that,
no one has played the game yet.
It seems as if she is waiting for someone to come.
So what's going on?

name: Overlord Asagi
description:
An evil Overlord that rules
the world of "Disgaea Wars (Tentative)".
She does anything that brings about
destruction, fear, and chaos.
A perfect example of evil Overlord.
People are scared of her,
but some are attracted to her bewitching appearance.
It's said that she even has an underground fan club.

name: Heroine Asagi
description:
The Heroine of "Disgaea Wars (Tentative)".
A cheerful, upright, and healthy girl
who fights bravely to save the world from
the clutch of the Overlord.
She has the same name of Asagi the Doomsday Overlord,
but shares only a bit of her appearance.
There is a noticeable difference, especially in the...
Oops, someone's coming.

name: Monster Hunter Meaver
description:
She makes her living by hunting the monsters all over the Netherworld.
She believes that she should change her clothes in line with her surroundings, as this will help keep her emotions high.
Sometimes she dresses up as a portal ferryman, and sometimes as a sailor. This time, she has put on her swimsuit in order to hunt down the sea monster.
She is cheerful and kind most of the time, but when she fights monsters or other hunters who intend to lay a finger on her pray, she becomes belligerent and unrelenting.
She prefers "Chocolate Coronets" over regular meals, and eating them on top of the fresh-slain monsters is considered a special treat by her.

name: Awakened Killia
description:
Supported by the Five Original Overlords,
Killia has overcome his
anger, sorrow, and troubled past.
He is no longer beset by his confusion, and his true power has awakened.
In this awakened state,
Killia's abilities have improved significantly.
That also includes his cooking skills,
if you know what I mean...
Such a miraculous boost should be called "awakening"!
The day Awakened Killia emerges,
would change the history of cooking.

name: Sea Club Owner Marlene
description:
The owner of the Sea Club.
The number of tourist has plummeted due to the monster incident, and the Sea Club  has fallen into financial difficulties, which worries Marlene.
However, she came up with the "treasure hunt" idea to attract new customers, and successfully attracted battle-seasoned adventurers who were interested in the treasure.
As a real virtuoso in slicing watermelons, she can slice through watermelons no matter what she is holding in her hand.

name: Fake Zenon
description:
Proclaiming himself to be Zenon,
this wretched middle-aged demon took Rozalin,
the true incarnation of Zenon, as his daughter.
This is how he satisfied his desire
for vengeance and vanity.
He destroyed Snow Melody Village,
Rozalin's homeland, and therefore was seen as
a sworn enemy by Fubuki and Yukimaru.
He feeds on the consciences of humans,
and will rise from the ashes no matter how many times he is defeated,
though he was eventually eradicated by awakened Zenon once and for all.
As a result, nobody ever knew his true name.

name: Salvatore
description:
A powerful girl and a member of the Diez Gentleman in the Evil Academy, a title only for the cream of the delinquent students.
Although a girl, somehow she has been widely accepted as a gentle "man".
Domineering and prone to force others to carry out her whimsical orders, she is extremely difficult to get along with.

name: Barbara
description:
Laharl's vassal.
Originally a member of the anti-Laharl faction, she swore allegiance to Laharl after a series of events.
Passive and obedient, she will never do anything if no one has given her orders.
Although she seems to be making an effort to think and act on her own...

name: Lucy
description:
A mysterious fallen angel appearing out of nowhere.
She seems to be hunted by demons,
though the way she talks and acts is extremely suspicious.
What? You said she appeared in the last scene of the EP 1 story,
and at that time she said she was going to conduct an undercover investigation?
Spoiler alert!

name: Diez
description:
A self-proclaimed Fallen Angel Hunter, he seems to be chasing down Lucy, a totally small-time villain.
However, his words and actions are somewhat awkward.
Supposedly, he is another undercover investigator just like Lucy...
Hey, you will keep your mouth shut, right?
Please keep this matter a secret for my sake!

name: Raspberyl XENO
description: A mysterious girl from another world, looking exactly as Raspberyl. She plays with her smartphone all the time. Is that ok, Raspberyl XENO...? XENO is read as "Zeno".

name: Mao XENO
description:
A mysterious boy from another world, looking exactly like Mao.
He, too, followed Saint Etna and arrived in this Netherworld.
He has invented his own evil gymnastics and will work out whenever he's idle.
By the way, he's nicknamed "Mao Mao".

name: Firework Master Hibana
description:
A firework master who is obsessed with developing new innovative fireworks.
Of course, fireworks are essential for the summer fest.
She attends the fest because she sees it as her perfect opportunity to show off her splendid works.
She is intending to create unprecedented Sardine Fireworks, but it seems that her lack of inspiration has prevented her from doing so.

name: Meliodas
description:
Despite his youthful appearance,he is 
actually the Dragon Sin of Wrath and 
captain of the Seven Deadly Sins,as well as 
the owner of the renowned tavern Boar Hat.

name: Elizabeth
description:
The third adoptive princess of the Kingdom of Liones.
A crybaby she might appear,
she actually has a strong will and a benevolent heart.
She is able to unleash incredible healing powers
when she is eager to save others.

name: Ban
description:
The Fox Sin of Greed of the Seven Deadly Sins,
known for his fox-patterned tattoo
and his immortality.
He will do whatever it takes to steal anything that interests him,
but pays no heed to anything else.

name: Diane
description:
The Serpent Sin of Envy of the
Seven Deadly Sins.
Despite her lack of magic abilities,
she is unparalleled
when it comes to strength.
Among her kindreds,
she is a rare peace-loving girl.

name: Gowther
description:
The Goat Sin of Lust
of the Seven Deadly Sins.
Unisex in appearance,
he is always indifferent and unemotional.

name: Merlin
description:
The Boar Sin of Gluttony of the
Seven Deadly Sins.
She is regarded as the
greatest sorceress in Britannia.

name: King
description:
The Grizzly Sin of Sloth of the Seven Deadly Sins,
and the king of fairies.

Since the moment he met Diane 700 years ago,
he has been in love with her.

name: Hawk
description:
Despite his rude way of talking, he is actually a warm-hearted piggy.
He speaks human language and
gets rid of the leftovers in the Boar Hat.

name: Mid-Boss
description:
His real name is “Vyers the Dark Adonis”, however, it has become "Mid-Boss", since Laharl ruthlessly said, "Who gives a damn about you? Your new name is Mid-Boss."
Actually, His true identity is Laharl's father, a close friend of Archangel Lamington, King Krichevskoy himself.
In addition, he is the only one in this world, who has earned Etna's respect.

name: Cute Flonne
description:
The leader of the Cutie V
in a red uniform, of course!
Because the leader of a group always
wears red!
As an advocator of love, she protects all kinds of love,
from the trivial love for crab miso to the extraordinary love for the entire universe!
To prepare for the final battle against the evil force,
she started recruiting new members.
She has found two promising talents!
In order to help them become qualified rangers,
Cute Flonne enrolled them into the reserves of the Cutie V
and is infusing them with the true essence of love!

name: Cute Chacha
description:
She was busy picking peaches on a towering cliff
when her athletic potential was appreciated by Cute Flonne,
who later convinced her to join
the Cutie V as its first reserve member.
She loves her carefree life
and was reluctant to join the Cutie V at first,
but after hearing that she could enjoy
as much catnip and other snacks as she please,
she was eventually persuaded.
Knowing that she can't enjoy snacks
until she accepts training and preaches
about the greatness of love and justice,
she has no choice but to stay in the Cutie V as a reserve member.

name: Cute Mei Ling
description:
The second reserve member of the Cutie V,
she has a zeal for mustard sauce
and will add it to whatever she eats
Her love for mustard sauce is so overwhelming
that she has even invented her own spells to protect it
and has been preaching about her love for mustard sauce,
though no one really pays much attention.
Cute Flonne was deeply touched
by her unconditional love for mustard and
invited her to the Cutie V.
Believing that joining the Cutie V will boost her popularity,
and that the denizens of the Netherworld
will be helping her protect her precious mustard sauce,
she accepted Cute Flonne's invitation.

name: Matt
description:
A human who was illuminated by the light from
Matt's Dark Mirror and accidentally arrived at the Netherworld.
He soon became widely known as a splendid model and singer,
rising to fame in all fields.
His special makeup, known as Matt's Makeup, was extremely popular in all Netherworlds!
Seeing his cherished
Dark Mirror
tainted by the corruption in the Netherworld
and used to commit numerous crimes,
he is feeling heartbroken.
By the way,
one of his dreams is to cast spells.

name: Zed
description:
A zombie boy who uses teleportation spell called "Super Reincarnation" to travel across Netherworlds on his quest to defeat the God of Destruction.
He comes across as extremely bubbly, but he is, in fact, a rather calm zombie.
Rumor has it that during his countless reincarnations and victories over the God of Destruction, his heart hardened, making him become rude and violent.

Please find more details in Disgaea 6, coming soon!

name: Majolene
description:
Known as the Witch of the Abyss, she is also the principal of the Magimage School of Magic.
She may look like just a cute little witch, but her power is the real deal!
Those who dare to cross her will be severely punished by her spells.

name: Zed
description:
Class: Zombie

A sharp-eyed zombie boy
who seems to have his own difficulties...

name: Cerberus
description:
Class: Zombie Dog

Zed's partner.
Although not good at fighting,
he will try to help Zed in any way he can.

name: Overlord Ivar
description:
Class: Overlord

He claimed to be the greatest and
strongest Overlord in the entire universe.

name: Torachiyo
description:
A battle-seasoned adventurer
who has dedicated her entire life to rice balls.
She literally cares about nothing but rice balls.
Is someone calling out for the King of Rice Balls?!
Why does she love rice balls so much?
Actually, there's a very sad story
behind her obsession with rice balls,
but we'll talk about it next time!

name: Des X
description:
The ultimate weapon created by Fuka's father,
Genjuro Kazamatsuri.
She once went toe-to-toe with Fuka and Desco,
but they buried the hatchet after a fierce battle.
And so,
the fearsome world conqueror trio,
Fuka, Desco and Des X,
have started their conquest.
Even now, she and Desco still
fight for the title of
the true final boss.

name: Genjuro Kazamatsuri
description:
Fuka's father,
a mad scientist who
created Desco and Des X
using the demon cells
he obtained from the Netherworld.
He is actually a
good(?) father who wants to his daughter's
dream of conquering the world.

name: Taro
description:
Adell's younger brother who lives in Holt Village.
His parents were already demonized when he was conceived,
so he was born with the appearance of a demon.
Currently, he's training relentlessly,
with a view to becoming
Rozalin's worthy vassal.

name: Hanako
description:
Adell's younger sister
who lives in Holt Village. Just like her elder brother Taro,
her parents were already demonized when she was conceived,
so she was born with the appearance of a demon.
In order to become an outstanding Majin,
she has become Etna's disciple with a promising future.

name: Zed
description:
The protagonist of Disgaea 6,
the latest addition to the Disgaea Series.
Disgaea 6 will be officially launched on January 28th, 2021!
It is available for pre-order now!

name: Sicily XENO
description:
Another Sicily from another world, proclaiming to be an Overlord and wearing an iconic (?) accessory for Overlords: a red scarf.
The rings on her both hands allow her to cast extremely powerful skills.
Each of these rings has its own name, and whenever Sicily XENO casts a skill, she calls out the name of the ring with all her might.
Because she believes “This will make me more impressive!
Ha-Hahahaha!!"
By the way, she remembers the names of the rings that she often uses, but she can't really recall the names of the rarely used ones.

name: Thunderlord Laharl
description:
Another Laharl from another world.
Dressed in white, he carries the aura of a gentleman.
His serious and earnest disposition does not really give the impression of a demon.
He wields the power of lightning when he fights, hence his title "Thunder Lord".
He is tasked to protect Saint Etna from being kidnapped by the XENO Clan, but the real reason for coming to this world seems to be his younger sister.

name: Dark Santa Usalia
description:
Usalia, who has inherited Laharl's Dark Santa Suit.
Perhaps because of her overly kind nature, she was particularly prone to the corruption of the Dark Santa Suit, and now she has become a grim and cruel demoness.
As one of the Five Original Overlords, Usalia possesses overwhelming power.
Now under the influence of the Dark Santa Suit, her true power is no longer confined by her benevolence towards this world, and she has become immensely powerful!
The Dark Santa Suit is indeed terrifying...

name: Tink
description:
A demon with a dual personality, Rozalin's childhood friend.
Once a beautiful and elegant boy, now he has become as ugly as a frog.
He is gentle and polite (?) most of the time, but when he gets angry, his body will turn red and he will start wreaking havoc. He is a dangerous monster.
Once again, Tink has failed to find a girlfriend this year and will have to spend his Christmas alone.
In the end, he bought an extra-large Christmas roast chicken so that he could at least enjoy the Christmas spirit.

name: Sakuya, Mother of the Netherworld
description:
Despite her youthful appearance, she is actually a battle-hardened senior Nine-Tails.
She has made divination her life's work, believing that the results of divination must not be defied.
Her belief makes her a troublemaker, as she will always try to make the results come true using her own powers.
She will curse those who get terrible divination results, and grant her favor to those who get ideal results.

name: Sweet Omega
description:
In the Love Laboratory, the most classic, authoritative, and popular love is a school romance.
She participated in the contest for the heroine and won the championship.
As an expert of romance, her impeccable school love performances have given many boys a taste of the sweet and sour sides of love.

name: Tria
description:
Her full name is Tria Izzy von DeBrueck, the daughter of the Lord who rules DeBrueck.
Distressed by the tyranny of her father, Orton Izzy von DeBrueck, she was on her way to an audience with the king when she was attacked by assassins sent by her father.
That's pretty much her character.
As a charming demoness, she excels at luring men into "rescuing" her.

name: Merome Romero
description:
A zombie girl loves horror stories but is somehow afraid of ghosts.
She used to cry like "Gyaah! That's so scary ♥" and throws herself into the arms of the man nearby. Such scene has happened myriads of times.
And numerous men was captured.
Sadly, it is the nature of men that makes them simply can't resist her.

name: Melodia
description:
A princess who dreams of having a beautiful love story.
She's always looking forward to
her own happy ending.
She loves to sing and
sings whenever she sees fit.
As for why she calls Zed her fiancé,
please find more information in Disgaea 6!

name: Overlord Ivar
description:
The self-proclaimed greatest Overlord
in the entire universe... probably.
While he does possess amazing power,
his hopeless stupidity
denies him any respect at all.

name: Subaru Natsuki
description:
A boy abruptly summoned to Emilia's world and thrust into a situation beyond his comprehension.
Yet, despite his ignorance, incompetence, inadequacy, and recklessness, he faces his harsh fate with a bold and fearless nature, even while complaining about the adversities he faces in the Netherworld.

name: Emilia
description:
A beautiful half-elf girl with silver hair and purple eyes, much like the "Witch of Envy" who nearly destroyed the world.
She is caring and generous to a fault, although she won't admit it.
She is said to be one of the Overlord Candidates for the next royal selection.

name: Rem
description:
A maid working at the mansion where Emilia and her friends live who performs all general duties on her own.
It is thanks to her that the estate continues to function.
She is one of the remaining survivors of the demon tribe who were known for their powers even amongst the demi-humans.
She adores her twin sister Ram.

name: Ram
description:
Rem's older twin sister and a maid working at the mansion where Emilia and her friends live.
She leaves most of the cooking, laundry, sewing, and cleaning to Rem.
Once a prodigy of the demon tribe, she possessed unrivaled powers.
However, she was robbed of her powers when she lost her "horn".

name: Puck
description:
A spirit contracted to Emilia.
It is a fire spirit, one of the Four Great Spirits possessing immense powers.
Its usual form is that of a small gray cat with round eyes and a pink nose.
It considers itself Emilia's guardian and is always by her side.

name: Beatrice
description:
A young girl working as the caretaker of the Forbidden Library in the mansion where Emilia and her friends live.
She looks adorable and wears an extravagant dress.
Although arrogant, she is also easily offended and does not get along with Subaru.

name: Sister Prier
description:
An active tomboy who was raised in an orphanage after losing her parents at a young age.
Her admiration for the Saint of Light led her to join the "Church of the Saint". After passing the exam, she officially became one of the La Pucelle nuns, specializing in exorcisms.
Her dream is to become a Saint of Light.
She has a strong sense of justice, and is highly qualified to perform exorcisms, but her actions are far from nun-like.
Hand-to-hand combat is her forte.

name: Croix
description:
A freelance exorcist who has accompanied Prier and her friends ever since a certain incident.
He travels from place to place trying to regain his lost memories.
A cheerful and reliable individual.

name: Alouette
description:
A nun in charge of educating Prier and Culotte as their senior in La Pucelle.
Her strong religious devotion can at times leads to a rigid inflexibility.
She is cautious and calm in the way she handles things.

name: Eclair
description:
Princess of the Kingdom of St. Paprika.
As a "Saint of Light" candidate, she is burdened by the high expectations of those around her.
Prier and Culotte have been her best friends for the past few years, and she affectionately refers to Prier as "Big Sister".

name: Culotte
description:
Prier's younger brother and a fellow member of La Pucelle.
He is always being pushed around by his older sister because of his shy and earnest personality.
He has a crush on Alouette.

name: Overlord Priere
description:
A powerful Overlord who is the spitting image of Prier.
She can be differentiated by the fact she shows more skin than Prier.
They both share similar personalities, but Overlord Priere hides an immense dark power.

name: Lanzarote
description:
A glamorous idol of the Netherworld.
She performs on tour all around the Netherworld, her popularity exceeding that of some Overlords.
She's an idol who sings, dances, and fights.
Currently serving under Overlord Laharl, she also has a personal relationship with Sicily who is a fan of hers.

name: Nagi
description:
A young girl who utilizes a special skill called Mechanology to summon Fuka and Desco and stop the war which took place in the human world.
She encountered Artina when she was still a nun and Valvatorez when he was still a tyrant.
In fact, it was none other than her who showed Valvatorez the wonders of sardines...
Or at least that's the story, but Valvatorez himself is actually not particularly fond of sardines.
Only she, Fuka, and Desco know the truth.

name: Mom
description: Adell's mother-in-law living in Holt Village. Once a human, she was cursed by Zenon and became a demon. So, her past memories as a human are hazy.

name: Diez Gentleman
description: Glorified as a legend among legends, they are the backbone of the senior students of the Evil Academy. Despite the existence of female members, they call themselves gentlemen. Once affiliated with Super Hero Aurum, now they belong to the Evil Academy but take orders from no one.

name: Three Heroes of the Netherworld
description:
An elite force that is part of the Netherworld Government.
They are made up of three members: Thunder Emperor Psylos, Tromayer the Atrocious, and Baltis the Dreadful.
They symbolize fear in the human world.

name: Four Devas of the Netherworld
description: The rest is omitted.

name: Seven Yakshas of the Netherworld
description: The rest is omitted.

name: Ten Kings of the Netherworld
description: The rest is omitted.

name: Love Zed
description:
The new form of Des X containing Super Overlord Love Cells developed by Mao.
With parental love, rather than romantic love, for Genjuro and the sisterly love of the Kazamatsuri sisters as a driving force, she brings out the best qualities of the Super Overlord Love Cells.
In other words, she is the embodiment of love who lives for love!

name: Cerberus
description: A dog who lives with Zed and his sister. He has all the appearances of a regular canine, but (according to him) he's actually a pretty big deal. He is at times doggy, and at others a self-proclaimed "super...something". What is his true identity? Play "Disgaea 6: Defiance of Destiny" to find out!

name: Bieko
description:
Zed's younger sister, idolized by both Zed and Ivar.
Her destructive power softens even Zed's sharp tongue.
Want to know how adorable Bieko is?
Play "Disgaea 6: Defiance of Destiny" to find out!

name: Piyori Nijino
description:
She comes from the world of TV and plays the role of Red in "Prism Rangers." While struggling with falling ratings, she does her best to carry out justice for children every day.
Just how educational is "Prism Rangers"?
Why is Piyori always alone?
Play "Disgaea 6: Defiance of Destiny" to find out!

name: Axirogue
description:
Axel who calls himself a Villainous Rogue Ranger.
Just because he has a character intro, it doesn't mean a new costume or new super powers.
He's just plain old Axel inside and out.

name: Misedor
description:
A king of the Human World who wields his wealth and power to send many heros to fight the God of Destruction.
He is someone who can truly say, "Money is not a problem!" He became a sponsor to the "Prism Rangers," and some argue the performance of the show improved due to his astounding financial investment.
What power can be bought with overwhelming wealth?
Play "Disgaea 6: Defiance of Destiny" to find out!

name: Emizel XENO
description:
Another Emizel who arrived from an alternate dimension.
He secured the position of an Elite Officer within XENO thanks to the help of his parents' connections.
Currently under stress from being in middle management, caught between obnoxious subordinates and terrifying senior managers, he struggles to prove he's worth more than his parents' connections.
His favorite gun is said to have been confiscated from enemy hands and illicitly remodeled to fit his needs.

name: Saint Etna
description:
A Saint who arrives from an alternate dimension and looks exactly like Etna.
The XENO have attacked her numerous times without any explanation.
She is said to have been helping Mao's research after being attacked by Mao XENO.
What were the results?

name: Flamelord Majorita
description:
Another Majorita who was summoned from an alternate dimension.
As one of the Holy Defenders, she carries the title of "Flamelord." Always full of life and vigor, her eyes sparkle with purity.
Seeing battle as an extension of play, she loves to battle and have fun.

name: Frostlord Rozalin
description:
Another Rozalin who was summoned from an alternate dimension.
As one of the Holy Defenders, she carries the title of "Frostlord." Her abilities are well known.
Although having a reputation as an ice queen, her mind is apparently filled with vague thoughts.
She also happens to have a sweet tooth.

name: Mao XENO
description:
A training-obsessed Mao who arrived from an alternate dimension.
He came to challenge Mao to a rematch after creating "Evil Gymnastics Part 2." Recently, he has been working hard to not only improve himself but also to promote his training regime.
His nickname is "Mao Mao."

name: Raspberyl XENO
description:
Another Raspberyl who arrived from an alternate dimension.
Always carrying her phone with her, she takes pictures and videos whenever she finds something interesting, and posts them on social media.
She came for fun, after hearing Mao XENO was attempting a rematch.

name: Fuka XENO
description:
Another Fuka who arrived from an alternate dimension.
A violent girl responsible for creating Desco XENO, blowing up bombs, and throwing Faceballs.
Desco XENO was previously damaged and is currently undergoing repairs.
It seems she has also cut her hair short.
Why?

name: Tink XENO
description:
Childhood friends with Emizel XENO and the embodiment of worldly ambitions.
Bribing his subordinates with money and violence, they join him today in his objective to seize Saint Etna in order to take Emizel XENO's position.
Although extremely proud to be implemented before the original Tink, he doesn't have any special privileges.

name: Sicily XENO
description:
Another Sicily who proclaims to be an Overlord and wears the iconic (?) Overlord scarf.
She came as Tink XENO's bodyguard to challenge her brother Laharl to a rematch.
She wears a ring on all ten fingers, each possessing the ability to invoke a powerful skill.
Her personal favorites are the "Burning Sirius" on her right index finger and the "Radiant Polaris" on her right middle finger.

name: Fallen Vessel Flonne
description:
A young girl with an ominous aura who looks like Flonne.
Details about her are shrouded in mystery...

name: Emizel XENO
description:
Another Emizel who secured the position of an Elite Officer within XENO thanks to the help of his parents' connections.
While struggling in middle management, he was caught by Mao's XENO Capture and is now being used as a guinea pig for terrifying experiments.
Will he be able to escape with the help of Tink XENO?
What does tomorrow hold for Emizel XENO?

name: Tink XENO
description:
Another Tink who is childhood friends with Emizel XENO and the embodiment of worldly ambitions.
He abandoned his master for a promotion, but with his future position on the line, he returned to help Emizel XENO as a means of keeping his career on track.
Although extremely proud to be implemented before the original Tink, he doesn't have any special privileges.

name: Levi
description:
He is the squad captain of the Scout Regiment in his own world.
He is widely known as humanity's strongest soldier, and is referred to as "Captain" by his comrades.

name: Mikasa Ackerman
description:
She has been by Eren's side ever since he saved her life when she was a child.
Protecting Eren means everything to her, and she wears the scarf he gave her at all times.

name: Eren Jeager
description:
A boy who yearns to explore the world beyond the wall.
After joining the Cadet Corps, he aims for a post in the Scout Regiment who is attempting to expand past the wall.
He is strong-willed and rushes headlong into danger.

name: Sweet Omega
description:
A girl in charge of romantic school comedies at the Love Laboratory.
She has a solid grip on the title of heroine for her ever-popular
performances in school-themed plays, and is head of the Love Laboratory.
She has given many men bitter-sweet memories with her classic romantic performances, and is an expert on youthful romance.
Despite her made-up character, she is apparently an honest and genuine person.

name: Tria
description:
Tria Izzy von DeBrueck.
Daughter of the Lord who rules DeBrueck.
Distressed by the tyranny of her father, Orton Izzy von DeBrueck, she was on her way to an audience with the king when she was attacked by assassins sent by her father.
That is her standard storyline.
Some think her status is part of the storyline, but she apparently really is a lady from a frontier region.
She may, or may not have a sister.

name: Merome Romero
description:
A maid zombie who doesn't like ghosts.
She is an ace of haunted houses.
She screams, "No, I'm scared!"
and grabs onto a man's arm, a trick she has repeated tens of thousands of times.
Men who encounter this trick inevitably protect her.
How sad that men are not allowed to break free from Merome's trap...

name: Swimsuit Raspberyl
description:
Raspberyl has arrived at Misedor's private beach to check out the School of the Weird.
She thought, "Delinquents had better observe the school rules" so she started to put on a school-designated swimsuit, but various people said, "You're a teacher so you don't have to wear the school swimsuit" and "It might actually look lascivious," so she decided not to.
The boat that she always carries around is extraordinary, having been inflated by Dean Mao himself and rebuilt!

name: Swimsuit Fuka
description:
With a newly made, snow white swimsuit, Fuka followed along to check out the School of the Weird and fully enjoy that summer.
She was asked for a guardian's seal required for the school visit, but she had Valvatorez be a guardian, and got his signature.
The Prinny sun visor and sandals are handmade and came with the application signature.

name: Amane
description:
A maiden appeared on this desert island, one who loves and lives in the sea.
She lives off seafood, and she has traversed many seas, sometimes getting tossed about by raging waves.
Apparently she established a rule for herself that loincloths are the formal dress of the sea.

name: Swimsuit Lucy
description:
As a result of working hard and bravely on a case, she got a tan.
No matter what anyone says, she's an undercover agent.
There is no way whatsoever
that she was just swimming all the time.
Her swimsuit accentuates her figure so much that people ask suspiciously where she bought it.
It is her professional attire.
She is undercover on a case, so it's a secret from her
coworkers Diez and Torachiyo.

name: Prophetess Plum
description:
A prophetess said to be able to see into the future.
Gifted with both a brilliant mind and magic powers, she took her father's Netherworld from him when she was just two years old.
Although new to being an Overlord, her talents have attracted the attention of other Overlords.
Her hobby was using Overlord Zetta as her toy, but she seems to have found a new potential toy.

name: Overlord Zetta
description:
He has thwarted a few thousand assassination attempts.
As the lead character of Phantom Kingdom and the strongest Overlord in the cosmos, he has forced many a usurper to bend the knee.
He strongly believes that "power is justice" and "love is for the weak." However, he cannot seem to follow through when it involves Salome and Petta.

name: Overlord Petta
description:
Overlord Zetta's daughter who arrived from the future.
She originally came to prevent a future where she and her father disappear.
Although already an Overlord, she is oddly polite and kind-hearted for a demon.
She has mastered her father's iconic beam and is still training under him.

name: Lady Salome
description:
Former human who fell into the underworld and became an Overlord.
An apprentice to Overlord Zetta, some say her magic powers exceed that of her master.
She is a woman of determination with love for Zetta greater than life itself.
When first meeting Petta, she mistook her for Zetta's illegitimate child, causing her to nearly have a stroke.
She now loves Petta as if she were her own daughter.

name: Demon Emperor Royal King Drake III
description:
A homeless Overlord who wanders the universe after losing his own Netherworld.
Despite being an Overlord, he is incredibly stingy.
He once crossed dimensions to take a position as an art teacher at Evil Academy.
Additionally, when he previously appeared, he...
You know, if you really want to know, you should see for yourself.
According to Zetta, "It's not worth explaining.
He's just plain stupid."

name: Demon Emperor Royal King Drake III
description:
Now do you see?
He really is just plain stupid.

name: Siedl, Lord of Hades
description:
A former hero who fell into the underworld.
He now rules as Lord of Hades.
He despises every living thing in this world and constantly harbors a deep grudge.
He apparently has a troubled history with Salome and has now expanded his hit list to include Zetta and Petta.

name: Dark Lord Valvolga
description:
A spectacular dark lord with the upper body of Demon General Micky, Fallen Angel Ophelia at its stomach, and Dryzen the Brutal Beast from the waist down.
A very popular Overlord who receives many invitations from different worlds as the Final Boss.
This time, he arrives as one of the fighters for the Top-Tier Battle (lmao).
Micky is the one who makes decisions, but he is always pushed around by the other two due to his weak-mindedness.

name: Wise
description:
An all-knowing and all-powerful Sage of the Netherworld.
She manages the Depository facility which connects directly to the Item World.
Although she comes across as the clever type, there are rumors that her teaching style is suspiciously solicit and that she is something of a know-it-all.
Despite her attempts, she cannot seem to shake off the suspicions that she is not entirely "all-knowing and all-powerful." Hang in there, Wise!

name: Timmy
description:
One of the few top breeders of the Netherworld and a passionate Beastmaster of monsters.
He is well-versed in the caring of the Innocent which he manages at the Innocent Ranch.
He and the ranch monsters are inseparable, and he won't take kindly to anyone who mocks them.
He spends so much time with the monsters that he often uses their cries to express his emotions.

name: Keke
description:
A follower of the god Dulvalkie, he is a sorcerer of the Netherworld whose appointed task is to control the fortunes and misfortunes of others.
He visits Etna after hearing he can control the fate of the greatest trainer if he remains in the Summer Retreat.
He ends up the boss of the Equipment Workshop where equipment is refined.
Although he may appear tricky, he is actually a sweetheart.
He will attack enemies with silly curses and support allies with equally silly spells...probably.

name: Aiko
description:
A female combat android.
Apparently, her official name is AICO-666.
Seeking to increase her power, she traverses the universe alone.
However, after hearing of one who seeks to be the greatest Overlord, she makes her way to the Summer Retreat where she meets Etna.
She currently manages the Request Board where she posts Etna's requests.
Although seen as a combat weapon, she is a multi-talented android who can cook, do the laundry, and look after the house.

name: Genjuro Kazamatsuri
description:
Occupation: mad scientist.
He is Fuka's father, and evil inventions are his forte.
He created the Ultimate Weapon DESCO to appease his daughter who wanted a high-performance sister and to achieve world domination.
Although Fuka could be a difficult daughter at times, as her father, he is forever devoted to her.

name: Des X
description:
The perfect version of the Ultimate Weapon DESCO, created by Genjuro Kazamatsuri.
The REAL Final Boss, Des X.
She once attempted to destroy all the annoying scum out there so that she could have "Dad" to herself.
Although Genjuro's love for Fuka grates on her nerves, she will happily follow "Dad" anywhere.

name: Kagemaru
description:
Another So-and-so-maru who arrived from an alternate dimension.
She believes in the motto "Assisted death before disgrace!" Assisted death for traitors!
Assisted death for deserters!
Assisted death for anyone who stands in my way!
What she really means by "assisted death" is simply lopping off their heads.
She left her old name behind along with her home, but she never quite got used to her new name.
What was she called before?

name: 鹿目まどか
description:
異世界からやって来た、
見滝原中学２年の少女。
現在は魔法少女として、
日々、魔女や使い魔と戦っている。
妙なゲートの先に行ってしまった
仲間たちを探しに、魔界へ。

name: 美樹さやか
description:
異世界からやって来た、
見滝原中学２年の少女。
まどかの同級生、かつ親友であり、
まどかやマミとともに、
魔法少女として魔女と戦っている。
まどかとともに、ゲートの先へ
仲間を追って来た模様。

name: 巴マミ
description:
異世界からやって来た、
見滝原中学３年の少女。
学生として、また魔法少女としても、
まどかたちの先輩にあたる。
まどかとともに、ゲートの先へ
仲間を追って来た模様。

name: キュゥべえ
description:
異世界からやって来た、
どう考えても可愛らしい
マスコットにしか見えないであろう、
謎の白い生命体。
願いごとを１つ叶える代わりに、
魔女と戦う魔法少女にする契約を
各地の少女たちと交わしている。
魔界に来た、その真意とは……？

name: 暁美ほむら
description:
異世界からやって来た、
見滝原中学２年の少女。
魔法少女でありながら、
キュゥべえを警戒し、
追って来たようだが……？

name: 佐倉杏子
description:
異世界からやって来た、
ほむらたちと同じ魔法少女。
